<section id="work_with_me">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-lg-12 wow fadeIn">
                <h4>Work With Us</h4>
                <hr class="colored">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
                <h5>“If you want to build a ship, don’t drum up the people to gather wood, divide the world, and give orders.  Instead, teach them to yearn for the vast and endless sea.”</h5>
                <h5>- Antoine de Saint-Exupery</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center content-row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                <div class="about-content">
                    <i class="fas fa-bullhorn fa-4x"></i>
                    <p class="majesti-book bigger">Coaching</p>
                    <p class="nexa-light smaller">As a trained coach by Coaches Training Institute, Stephanie will work one-on-one with you or any of your team members to unlock the power you need to grow your business and build the life you want.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                <div class="about-content">
                    <i class="far fa-comments fa-4x"></i>
                    <p class="majesti-book bigger">Speaking</p>
                    <p class="nexa-light smaller">Stephanie speaks on topics that around inspiration, leadership, habits, authenticity, and basically all things related to knowing your power.  If you’d like to book a talk, reach out.</p>
                </div>
            </div> 
        </div>
        <div class="text-center col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 wow fadeIn">
            <h5>Stephanie works with her business partner, Kara, to create experiences that change how people think and act:</h5>
        </div>
       
        <div class="row text-center content-row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                <div class="about-content">
                    <%= image_tag("wolfAndHeron.png", alt: "Wolf & Heron", class: "img-responsive center-block", id: "wolfAndHeronLogo") %>
                    <p class="majesti-book bigger">Wolf & Heron</p>
                    <p class="nexa-light smaller">At <%= link_to "Wolf & Heron", "http://www.wolfandheron.com/", target: "_blank" %>, we design experiences and workshops that are highly immersive, offering the next wave of leaders the opportunity to discover, share insights, and build capabilities in a fun, interactive way.</p>
                </div>
            </div> 
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                <div class="about-content">
                    <%= image_tag("cairnConcept.png", alt: "Carin Concept", class: "img-responsive center-block", id: "carinConceptLogo") %>
                    <p class="majesti-book bigger">The Cairn Concept</p>
                    <p class="nexa-light smaller">At <%= link_to "The Cairn Concept", "http://www.thecairnconcept.com/", target: "_blank" %>, we provide organizations with the strategies and tools they need to change the way their people think and act through a high-touch, customized, consultative approach.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>